description: Lists all contacts and escalation plans in Incident Manager.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token to continue to the next page of results.

nested_items.name: Contacts
nested_items.description: A list of the contacts and escalation plans in your Incident Manager account.

nested_items.name: ContactArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the contact or escalation plan.

nested_items.name: Alias
nested_items.description: The unique and identifiable alias of the contact or escalation plan.

nested_items.name: DisplayName
nested_items.description: The full name of the contact or escalation plan.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: Refers to the type of contact. A single contact is type PERSONAL and an escalation plan is type ESCALATION.
